trans-unit.source: Sphinx version: Please select the Sphinx version to be used.
Activate plugins: 3rd-party plugins you may use in your documents.
Deactivate unknown extensions: If ticked, faulty extensions will be deactivated to let the Sphinx compilation continue anyway.
PDF Builder: Please select the builder to use to render PDF.
Install rst2pdf: Locally build rst2pdf, additional gcc libraries are needed.
